#Asynchronous search query is usrf incase if the query is taking longer to process
#then, you can use asynchronous search query to run and come back later with the ID that it gives you and come back later to get the results 

SUBMIT:
Write the query:
_async_search accepts the same parameters and body as the _search API.

CHECK:
Check search status:
_async_search requests return an ID that can be used to check the search status.

RESULTS:
Get search results:
Search results can be fetched while _async_search executes and after it completes.

DELETE:
Delete the search:
Search results can be deleted when no longer needed.

